Problem Statement:
Given an array of numbers find the index of the pivot.

Code:

n=int(input())
t=n
L=[]
while(t):
    L.append(int(input())
    t-=1
sum1=0
sum2=0
for i in range(0,n):
    if(i==0 or i==n-1):
        continue
    for j in L[0:i]:
        sum1+=j
    for k in L[i+1:]:
        sum2+=k
    if(sum1==sum2):
        print(i)
        break
    sum1=0
    sum2=0
